{"word":"παρεκβαίνω","slug":"παρεκβαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παρεκβαίνω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-βήσομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>παρεξέβην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a><a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>to step out aside from, deviate from</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to overstep, transgress</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to deviate</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>: <i>to make a digression</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}